          <p>This website has been reviewed and tested to function correctly. In principle, correct operation can be guaranteed 365 days a year, 24 hours a day. However, the Provider does not rule out the possibility that there may be certain programming and related errors, or that force majeure causes, natural disasters, strikes, or similar circumstances may occur that make access to the website impossible.</p>
