          <p>In general, access to information about the different products and services existing on the website, as well as its navigation will be free and gratuitous, therefore not requiring Users to register with the consequent delivery of their personal data, nor the use of keys or passwords. Notwithstanding the foregoing, certain sections of the website will require prior inclusion of data in forms or the relevant registration.</p>
          <p>The User undertakes to make adequate and lawful use of the website as well as the contents, products and services, in accordance with the applicable legislation at all times, these General Terms of Use of the website, morality and generally accepted good customs and public order.</p>
          <p>The User must refrain from:</p>
